org.orgName: District Court of the Third Judicial District of Washington Territory

body.p: Office of the Sheriff of King County Washington Territory

I William Cochrane Sheriff of King County W.T. do hereby certify that at the coming to me of the annexed writ of Habeas Corpus the said C.F. Reed was committed to my custody and is detained by virtue of the commitment which is hereto annexed. Nevertheless I have the body of the said C.F. Reed now here before the court as I am within commands.
Dated at Seattle W.T. this 27th day of Apr. 1888
William Cochrane Sheriff of King County W.T.
Sheriffs Fees Bringing up Prisoner 1.00 Travel .20 Return .50 $1.70
